<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">祈父</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson3f6243e9dfb7">
祈父，予王之爪牙。胡转予于恤，靡所止居？<br />祈父，予王之爪士。胡转予于恤，靡所厎止？<br />祈父，亶不聪。胡转予于恤？有母之尸饔。
</div>
</div>
<div class="tool">
<div class="shoucang"><iframe style="width:18px; height:30px; border:0px;" src="/shiwen2017/like.aspx?idsw=183&from=http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=3f6243e9dfb7"></iframe></div>
